       added/removed from the series file and from the qquuiilltt metadata.

       Any change on a binary file is not representable in a diff and will thus lead to a failure unless the maintainer deliberately decided to include that modified
       binary file in the debian tarball (by listing it in ddeebbiiaann//ssoouurrccee//iinncclluuddee--bbiinnaarriieess). The build will also fail if it finds binary  files  in  the  debian  sub-
