   FFoorrmmaatt:: 33..00 ((bbzzrr))
       This format is experimental. It generates a single tarball containing the bzr repository.

       EExxttrraaccttiinngg

       The tarball is unpacked and then bzr is used to checkout the current branch.

       BBuuiillddiinngg

       Before going any further, some checks are done to ensure that we don't have any non-ignored uncommitted changes.

       Then  the  VCS  specific part of the source directory is copied over to a temporary directory. Before this temporary directory is packed in a tarball, various
       cleanup are done to save space.

